  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Four crore worth of drug is seized",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police Media Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Mr. Nihal Talduwa said that the police special task force officers have arrested a person who was carefully hiding and transporting a stock of ice drug worth more than four crore rupees in a car in Wattala.",
        "Four kilos of ice drugs were found in the suspect's possession and taken into police custody.",
        "On the instructions of the Commander of the Police Special Task Force, DIG Attorney General Varuna Jayasundara, a team including the Station Commander of the Organized Crime Unit, Inspector CR Paramullage conducted the raid."
      ],
